==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Alkali metal
<hw>Alkali metal</hw>. <def>Any one of the univalent metals of group I
of the periodic table of the elements, including lithium, sodium,
potassium, rubidium, cesium, and francium. The hydroxides of these
metals are soluble in water and form strongly basic solutions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC.</source>]</p>

